data.description: Looking for the perfect family home? Look no further! This stunning property located in the desirable Millard School District is sure to impress. With 3 bed, 3 bath, and a 2 car garage, this home offers everything you need and more. Nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac, the house boasts a truly spectacular interior with modern SS appliances in the spacious kitchen. As the temperature drops, gather with loved ones in the cozy living room next to the fireplace that adds warmth and comfort to the room. The fully finished basement, complete with a 3/4 bath and laundry facilities, makes this home a real game-changer for families. The newer roof and siding and beautiful luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout only add to the meticulously maintained look of the house. Last but not least, the fully fenced backyard oasis, complete with a fire pit, makes for the perfect space to relax and unwind with friends and family. Don't miss your chance to own this move-in ready home, schedule your showing today!
